  "title": "Better Netherite and Smithing Crafting Recipe(BNASCR)",
  "description": "Adds a new crafting recipe for netherite and netherite upgrade to make it more affordable. And you can craft netherite smithing template. Plus adds slowly the those stuff to other mods with adds trims.",
  "body": "<div align=\"center\">\n\n# Better Netherite and Smithing Crafting Recipe\n**All-in-one netherite crafting & smithing template recipes**\n*No extra mods. No extra datapacks. Just one.*\n\n</div>\n\n<br/>\n\n<a href=\"https://fabricmc.net\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/fabric_vector.svg\" alt=\"Fabric\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://neoforged.net\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/neoforge_vector.svg\" alt=\"NeoForge\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://minecraftforge.net\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/forge_vector.svg\" alt=\"Forge\"></a>\n<a href=\"https://quiltmc.org\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/quilt_vector.svg\" alt=\"Quilt\"></a>\n\n<br/>\n\n![MC](https://img.shields.io/badge/🎮_MINECRAFT-1.20_–_1.21.11-1ABC9C?style=for-the-badge)\n![ENV](https://img.shields.io/badge/🖥️_Server_SIDE-2C3E50?style=for-the-badge)\n\n---\n\n> 🚨 **Alpha versions of 1.20 – 1.20.6 may not work properly.**\n> \n> 💡 Why download **2 mods/datapacks** when you can get it in **one**?\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies *(Mod Versions Only)*\n\n| Loader | Requires |\n|--------|----------|\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/fabric_vector.svg\" alt=\"Fabric\" height=\"40\"> | <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/requires/fabric-api_vector.svg\" alt=\"Fabric API\" height=\"40\"></a> |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/quilt_vector.svg\" alt=\"Quilt\" height=\"40\"> | None |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/forge_vector.svg\" alt=\"Forge\" height=\"40\"> | None |\n| <img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/supported/neoforge_vector.svg\" alt=\"NeoForge\" height=\"40\"> | None |\n\n---\n\n## Netherite Crafting Recipe\n\n**Shapeless** — place ingredients in any order\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/12a80343b0c2a8e2d1b154848d17df362903956a_0.webp\" width=\"480\"/>\n<br/><br/>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c36970e5a5db643d0a64ddb2977b8c1168c4047f_0.webp\" width=\"480\"/>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n## Smithing Template Crafting Recipe *(Actually balanced, unlike the old one with diamonds instead)*\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/1724ddcee4904a85316b68ea7e45d9e317ebbd38.png\" width=\"480\"/>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n<summary>🗃️ More Smithing Template Recipes</summary>\n\n<br/>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/40b1b56fef14e8ffea6cb70d86a2941e23c8844a_0.webp\" width=\"480\"/>\n</div>",
